1
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:51,790
Did you see clearly, Sister?

2
00:00:52,160 --> 00:00:55,950
The mountain god of this village has never been a deity,

3
00:00:56,250 --> 00:00:58,200
but an evil spirit I raised.

4
00:00:58,290 --> 00:01:00,660
I had the villagers sacrifice girls every year,

5
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:01,660
to feed it with living souls.

6
00:01:01,660 --> 00:01:03,830
This evil spirit has been waiting for you.

7
00:01:03,830 --> 00:01:06,330
Even if your arrival at Luoxia Village was an accident,

8
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:09,080
from the moment you saw that child on the altar,

9
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:10,910
you were destined to walk into this mountain,

10
00:01:10,910 --> 00:01:12,500
and come before me.

11
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:13,830
After a thousand years,

12
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:15,200
how could I not know you?

13
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,660
What exactly do you want?

14
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:19,630
Why involve these innocent villagers and children?

15
00:01:20,910 --> 00:01:21,660
To lure me here,

16
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:22,870
you took so many lives.

17
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:25,470
Aren't you afraid your soul will be destroyed?

18
00:01:27,330 --> 00:01:30,080
I have waited a thousand years for this day.

19
00:01:37,370 --> 00:01:40,160
Do you two really think you can stop me?

20
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:46,400
I'll block it, you find a chance to fight back.

21
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,900
Those who stand in my way will die!

22
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:04,330
As long as I have a breath left, I won't let you succeed.

23
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,830
Together, we will never lose to you!

24
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:14,000
This lamp is more troublesome than I thought.

25
00:02:14,790 --> 00:02:17,250
Stop pretending to protect her.

26
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:20,079
Back then, it was because of you that she ended up

27
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,660
losing her body and soul.

28
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,090
What did you say?

29
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,370
No!

30
00:02:56,329 --> 00:02:58,870
Deng!

31
00:03:36,579 --> 00:03:37,660
Deng! Deng!

32
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:39,250
Wake up, don't scare me.

33
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:49,660
We were originally one,

34
00:03:50,329 --> 00:03:51,450
but why?

35
00:03:58,540 --> 00:03:59,600
Fellow villagers,

36
00:03:59,829 --> 00:04:01,410
you have all been deceived.

37
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:04,330
There has never been a mountain god protecting the village,

38
00:04:04,330 --> 00:04:07,000
only an evil spirit that feeds on the souls of children.

39
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,000
The children sent into the mountain

40
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,380
were never protected.

41
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:12,500
They were all killed by the evil spirit.
